    "7. Top selling month"

    "def make_product_types(value):\n",
    "    battery = ['Batteries']\n",
    "    cable = ['Cable']\n",
    "    headphones = ['Headphones']\n",
    "    lcd = ['Moniter', 'TV']\n",
    "    phone = ['Phone', 'iphone']\n",
    "    laptop = ['Laptop']\n",
    "    electronics = ['Washing Machine', 'Dryer']\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if any(x in value for x in battery):\n",
    "        return 'Battery'\n",
    "    elif any(x in value for x in cable):\n",
    "        return 'Cable'\n",
    "    elif any(x in value for x in headphones):\n",
    "        return 'Headphone'\n",
    "    elif any(x in value for x in lcd):\n",
    "        return 'Display Device'\n",
    "    elif any(x in value for x in phone):\n",
    "        return 'Phone'\n",
    "    elif any(x in value for x in laptop):\n",
    "        return 'Laptop'\n",
    "    elif any(x in value for x in electronics):\n",
    "        return 'Electronic'\n",
    "    \n",
    "df['Product Type'] = df.Product.apply(make_product_types)"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    "## New ‘Sales’ column calculated from the ordered quantity and the price"
   ]

   "cell_type": "code",

   "id": "1c9e63c7",

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "8adc71e2",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Finding out the top selling product"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 165,
   "id": "e0015799",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",

     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "product_group = df.groupby('Product')\n",
    "quantity_ordered = product_group.sum()['Quantity Ordered']\n",
    "prices = df.groupby('Product').mean()['Price Each']\n",
    "products = [product for product, df in product_group]\n",
    "\"\"\"Visualization\"\"\"\n",
    "fig, ax1 = plt.subplots(figsize=(24, 14))\n",
    "ax2 = ax1.twinx()\n",
    "# AXES 1\n",
    "ax1.bar(products, quantity_ordered)\n",
    "ax1.set_title( # title\n",
    "    \"Most Sold Product\",\n",
    "    weight=\"bold\", # weight\n",
    "    fontsize=35, # font-size\n",
    "    pad=30 # padding\n",
    ")\n",
    "ax1.set_xlabel( # x-label\n",
    "    \"Product Names\",\n",
    "    weight=\"bold\", # weight\n",
    "    fontsize=25, # font-size\n",
    "    color=\"black\" # color\n",
    ")\n",
    "ax1.set_ylabel( # y-label\n",
    "    \"Quantity Ordered\", \n",
    "    color=\"blue\", # color\n",
    "    fontsize=20, # font-size\n",
    "    weight=\"bold\" # weight\n",
    ")\n",
    "ax1.set_xticklabels( # x-ticks\n",
    "    products, # ticks\n",
    "    rotation=\"vertical\", # rotation \n",
    "    weight=\"bold\" # weight\n",
    ")\n",
    "# AXES 2\n",
    "sns.lineplot( # plot\n",
    "    products, # x-axis\n",
    "    prices, # y-axis\n",
    "    color=\"red\"\n",
    ")\n",
    "ax2.set_ylabel( # y-label\n",
    "    \"Price in USD ($)\", \n",
    "    color=\"green\", # color\n",
    "    fontsize=20, # font-size\n",
    "    weight=\"bold\" # weight\n",
    ");"
   ]
